    Provides the SPx AV Server GUI classes.

    Provides utility classes such as the Ticker and Version classes.

      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  ClientsPanel
      AV Server ClientsPanel class, which displays a list of receiving clients together with information from one of the receiving clients.

      AV Server DistributionPanel class, which displays network distribution information and controls for a stream.
      class  EncPanel
      AV Server EncPanel class, a panel for showing encoder information with button to display applicable encoder dialog.
      class  LatencyPanel
      AV Server LatencyPanel class, a panel for displaying graphs of latency information.
      class  PreviewPanel

      AV Server PriorityPanel class, a panel for controlling stream priorities.
      class  RecordPanel
      AV Server RecordPanel class, a panel for displaying video recording information.
      class  SrcPanel
      AV Server SrcPanel class, a panel for showing source information with button to display applicable source dialog.
      class  StreamComponentPanel
      Declares the AV Server StreamComponentPanel class, base class for all panels that will be contained in a stream panel.
      class  StreamEncPanel
      AV Server StreamEncPanel class, panel that contains everything for the control of an encode stream.
      class  StreamPanel
      AV Server StreamPanel class, base class for all stream panels: StreamEncPanel, StreamReplayPanel, and StreamTestPanel.
      class  StreamReplayPanel
      AV Server StreamReplayPanel class, panel that contains everything for the control of an replay stream.
      class  StreamsPanel
      AV Server StreamsPanel class, panel that contains all the streams in a tabbed interface.
      class  StreamTestPanel
      AV Server StreamTestPanel class, panel that contains everything for the control of an test stream.
      class  SvrConnectPanel
      AV Server SvrConnectPanel class, panel that allows control over which remote AV server is controlled by the GUI.
      class  SvrHealthPanel
      AV Server SvrHealthPanel class, panel that displays health information from the connected AV server.
      class  SvrInfoPanel
      AV Server SvrInfoPanel class, panel that displays status information from the connected AV server.
      class  SvrPanel
      AV Server SvrPanel class, panel that controls connection to an AV server and displays information and controls associated with the currently connected server.
      class  SvrPriorityPanel
      AV Server SvrPriorityPanel class, panel that allows configuration of server wide priority settings.
      class  SvrRecordPanel
      AV Server SvrRecordPanel class, panel for control of multi-input recording.
      class  SvrReplayPanel
      AV Server SvrReplayPanel class, panel for control of multi-output file source.
      class  SvrSaveConfigPanel
      AV Server SvrSaveConfigPanel class, panel for saving the AV server configuration.
